feat: Add media extraction service for EXIF and music metadata
- Implemented ExtractionService to handle metadata extraction from media files. - Added methods for extracting EXIF data from images and ID3 tags from audio files. - Integrated extraction calls in CreateEmptyFile and CopyRecursively methods to trigger metadata extraction upon file creation and copying. - Enhanced setting service to include boolean retrieval for configuration flags. - Updated VFS service to support file reading for metadata extraction. - Introduced new constants for media extraction settings. - Improved error handling and logging for extraction processes.
